1️⃣ Extract Data
Run:python extract_data.py
This will create extracted_data.txt for reference.

2️⃣ Create Embeddings & Store in FAISS
Run:python create_embeddings.py
This will store the FAISS index in faiss_index/.

3️⃣ Run the Flask API
Run:python app.py
Your API will be available at:
http://127.0.0.1:5000/query

4️⃣ Test the API
Using Postman (Recommended)
Method: POST
URL: http://127.0.0.1:5000/query